        <updateDate>2007-03-03T17:20:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow accelerated cost recovery (i.e., a seven-year recovery period) for ethanol or biodiesel refining property. Defines &quot;ethanol or biodiesel refining property&quot; as property used to produce biodiesel and property used to produce ethanol other than from petroleum, natural gas, or coal (including lignite).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to classify ethanol and biodiesel refining property as 7-year property for purposes of the accelerated cost recovery system.</title>
